name: FloralMarbles_Model 1.5
description:
Model info

This is a dreambooth model trained with the data set of FloralMarble on top of stable diffusion 1.5, all creadits to spaablauw for original images.

I left several models uploaded, all the intermediate steps + two anime models that I merged into.

I would recomend try the 4000 steps model or the 7000 steps one, it depends a bit in what you want, I had relly good result in booth. For img2img 7000 step version is better.

Use whatever VAE you want.

Go to https://huggingface.co/N75242/FloralMarbles_Model for more model variantos like anime merge.

Tag list

Get the tag list images had here

I used "flrmrbl" as an unique token, so it should activate the model traing data, also "floral marble" is present in all images, but its more generic si probably less powerfull. But as an alternative use "in the style of flrmrbl" or "flrmrbl style".

Have fun!
